sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor User
    participant Streamlit
    participant LangGraph
    participant OpenAI
    participant Memory as Long-term Memory
    participant Store as RAG Vector Store

    User->>Streamlit: 이미지 + 초기 진단 입력
    Streamlit->>LangGraph: 실행 요청

    LangGraph->>OpenAI: 초기 진단 생성
    OpenAI-->>LangGraph: initial diagnosis

    LangGraph->>Memory: 유사 memory 검색
    Memory-->>LangGraph: memory candidates

    alt early exit hit
        LangGraph-->>Streamlit: memory 기반 결과 반환
    else no hit
        LangGraph->>Store: 유사 case 검색
        Store-->>LangGraph: retrieval candidates
        LangGraph->>OpenAI: 후보 grading
        OpenAI-->>LangGraph: relevant / not relevant

        loop 필요 시
            LangGraph->>OpenAI: query rewrite
            OpenAI-->>LangGraph: rewritten query
            LangGraph->>Store: 재검색
            Store-->>LangGraph: 새 후보
        end

        LangGraph-->>Streamlit: 최종 결과 반환
    end

    Streamlit-->>User: 결과 표시

    opt 전문가 피드백
        User->>Streamlit: 승인/반려
        Streamlit->>Memory: feedback 저장
    end